      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;welcome-here-fellow-wavelet-surfer&#34;&gt;Welcome here fellow wavelet surfer!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-is-this-blog-about&#34;&gt;What is this blog about?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This blog is mostly about applied and computational mathematics, with a specific focus on harmonic analysis and its applications for signal processing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I will present topics which I&amp;rsquo;m willing to explore, learn and share. Because sharing and presenting knowledge in a clear way is just as fun as learning.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
      
